race.comment: The local MATROOSHI (8) is the testing material. She found more like his best narrowly beaten here over 1400m and steps up to 1700m for the first time. Expect her to manage that well and Bates stays aboard. Stablemate TREMAMORE (7) peaks and is looking for this distance. She showed enough early doors to give her an each-way hope. SUPER SNITCH (9) is also racing short of his best but is third-up and has placed this course/distance. DUKE OF HASTINGS (2) resumes in a lesser grade and has jumped out twice at Flemington. Kicking off over this trip shouldn't be an issue and he has two key gear additions. Is likely to be running into it late.
